dc_title_s: Davies's new map of the British Metropolis: the boundaries of the boroughs, county court districts, railways and modern improvements; drawn and engraved ... by B.R. Davies.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Shows railways and those under construction. 1 map; 64 x 88 cm., folded to 34 x 50 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
